Xochipilli, the "Prince of Flowers," is god of beauty, happiness, music, and gambling. His twin sister is Xochiquetzal.
He is chaotic good. In his true form, he has the body of a young man, but his face is that of a decaying corpse. He is a member of the Aztec+pantheon. 

